{"word":"πλινθίον","slug":"πλινθίον","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>πλινθίον</b></el> <el>(πλινθίον, ου, τό,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:Diminutive'>Dim.</a> of <a href='S:πλίνθος'><el>πλίνθος</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a small brick</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>= <a href='S:πλαίσιον'><el>πλαίσιον</el></a>, <i>a rectangle</i> or <i>square</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}